data.description: Short Sale.  SHORT SALE.    Great value in this Spacious home with room for everyone.  Looking for a flexible layout with rarely available 6 bedrooms.  Recently updated with a fully fenced backyard, and kitchen granite.  The layout has a full bedroom and bathroom downstairs.  Large master bedroom features a walk in closet and bathroom with dual sinks, and walk in shower.  Additionally 4 rooms and a loft give you flexibility to have a home office, and make sure no one has to share a bedroom.  Upstairs laundry room is convenient and keeps you from having to lug up Excellent neighborhood with a   Community pool low hoa fees, nearby area schools and shopping.
